    "text": "BP 180.0/120 — প্রি-এক্লাম্পসিয়া! বাম কাতে শোয়ান, ১০৮ কল করুন।",
    "tone": "emergency",
    "key": "6a35e76a09cbebab186a6c26aaefd63a",
    "filename": "6a35e76a09cbebab186a6c26aaefd63a.mp3",
    "bytes": 44160
  },
  {
    "text": "Home care. Routine follow-up per module schedule. Counsel on warning signs. Record visit on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b381fda4cc7f24c3913deb0299baeb59",
    "filename": "b381fda4cc7f24c3913deb0299baeb59.mp3",
    "bytes": 37632
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC within 24 h. Follow up in 2 days. Counsel on escalation signs. Record on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "4c54a4883b569d43f7e55d4c8f14872a",
    "filename": "4c54a4883b569d43f7e55d4c8f14872a.mp3",
    "bytes": 37920
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer FRU/SNCU/DH immediately (≤ 30–60 min). Call 108. Bengali action card displayed. Decision trace locked and stored. MDSR hook triggered if applicable.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8c03b8fb58e3dbf569b60adfa5e2100d",
    "filename": "8c03b8fb58e3dbf569b60adfa5e2100d.mp3",
    "bytes": 62976
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু বুকের দুধ খেতে পারছে না?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "25166b728813c326cd93beee5582cbf7",
    "filename": "25166b728813c326cd93beee5582cbf7.mp3",
    "bytes": 11136
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately (≤ 30 min). Do not delay for any reason.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "5123f0864b80017982e6681e493d39d9",
    "filename": "5123f0864b80017982e6681e493d39d9.mp3",
    "bytes": 36192
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর শরীরে জ্বর আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6fbd3f7e4e74fa30b658e0ac33d808e6",
    "filename": "6fbd3f7e4e74fa30b658e0ac33d808e6.mp3",
    "bytes": 10368
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Any fever in a newborn is a danger sign.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "6d85c7021fcc51cf5540b61ee7dcf32c",
    "filename": "6d85c7021fcc51cf5540b61ee7dcf32c.mp3",
    "bytes": 34464
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাস-প্রশ্বাস দ্রুত বা কষ্টকর?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e4c61023f4ca7cdd95a2143f47cd00b6",
    "filename": "e4c61023f4ca7cdd95a2143f47cd00b6.mp3",
    "bytes": 12864
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Count RR — if ≥ 60/min = severe.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d52ef26f39d4d5353bde05dbaaa0ef38",
    "filename": "d52ef26f39d4d5353bde05dbaaa0ef38.mp3",
    "bytes": 73344
  },
  {
    "text": "নাভি লাল, ফোলা বা পুঁজ আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7c1e51baa030149a8ffbab913fa1469f",
    "filename": "7c1e51baa030149a8ffbab913fa1469f.mp3",
    "bytes": 16320
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Omphalitis can progress to sepsis within hours.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "48a1ff80688e308827c7c40ac092fa4f",
    "filename": "48a1ff80688e308827c7c40ac092fa4f.mp3",
    "bytes": 23808
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু অনেক কম নড়ছে বা নিস্তেজ?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "f70ba52272d026cdf31f9f5ed398e698",
    "filename": "f70ba52272d026cdf31f9f5ed398e698.mp3",
    "bytes": 13344
  },
  {
    "text": "PSBI hard-stop. Refer to SNCU/FRU immediately. Lethargy = severe systemic illness.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "0310356d95bd52bfff600c92830eaabc",
    "filename": "0310356d95bd52bfff600c92830eaabc.mp3",
    "bytes": 27264
  },
  {
    "text": "ত্বক হলুদ বা নীলাভ দেখাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "5ac25ce45230fc7c00de76c340d95dcb",
    "filename": "5ac25ce45230fc7c00de76c340d95dcb.mp3",
    "bytes": 12864
  },
  {
    "text": "Cyanosis or jaundice within 24 h = refer SNCU immediately. Jaundice day 2–14 without palm/sole involvement = refer PHC within 24 h for bilirubin check.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c47671ed25ef409864b02d275550b689",
    "filename": "c47671ed25ef409864b02d275550b689.mp3",
    "bytes": 58464
  },
  {
    "text": "সব প্রশ্নের উত্তর না — কোনো বিপদচিহ্ন নেই?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7ffebc618b452badf2f6e2de4e6f9822",
    "filename": "7ffebc618b452badf2f6e2de4e6f9822.mp3",
    "bytes": 25248
  },
  {
    "text": "HBNC home visit schedule: day 1, 3, 7, 14, 28. Counsel on exclusive breastfeeding, warmth, cord care, danger sign recognition.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3f1d8a6e3d5cb11355d5f6320ef7054d",
    "filename": "3f1d8a6e3d5cb11355d5f6320ef7054d.mp3",
    "bytes": 65184
  },
  {
    "text": "পাঁচ দিনের বেশি জ্বর চলছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b6710bc3615b55462e519934cdf665ab",
    "filename": "b6710bc3615b55462e519934cdf665ab.mp3",
    "bytes": 11616
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC/DH same day. Rule out malaria, typhoid, dengue. Do not give antipyretics and send home.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "82ee1a019acb374ee789ceab2bb83ae8",
    "filename": "82ee1a019acb374ee789ceab2bb83ae8.mp3",
    "bytes": 43872
  },
  {
    "text": "কাশি বা শ্বাসকষ্ট আছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "91236c0caa0d366405d7b61ee0e60910",
    "filename": "91236c0caa0d366405d7b61ee0e60910.mp3",
    "bytes": 11616
  },
  {
    "text": "Count respiratory rate. RR ≥ 50 (2–12 m) or ≥ 40 (1–5 y) = pneumonia → PHC within 24 h. Chest indrawing or stridor = severe pneumonia → RED, refer FRU immediately.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "4831cc5ced98262f8f772207594617da",
    "filename": "4831cc5ced98262f8f772207594617da.mp3",
    "bytes": 126720
  },
  {
    "text": "ডায়রিয়া বা বারবার বমি হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "9a28f9a481e33d261837737409b86bc6",
    "filename": "9a28f9a481e33d261837737409b86bc6.mp3",
    "bytes": 12864
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess dehydration. No dehydration = GREEN (ORS at home). Some dehydration = YELLOW (ORS at PHC). Severe dehydration (sunken eyes, skin pinch slow, unable to drink) = RED, IV fluids at FRU.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "860f5c6819418cffa5e0bda380c90e48",
    "filename": "860f5c6819418cffa5e0bda380c90e48.mp3",
    "bytes": 106560
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু খেতে একদম অস্বীকার করছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c6e7b111e951243d38677966bfa17098",
    "filename": "c6e7b111e951243d38677966bfa17098.mp3",
    "bytes": 12384
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess for illness cause. If associated with fever/diarrhoea = escalate to relevant rule. Isolated feeding refusal > 2 days = PHC referral within 24 h.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b4830736a1d78bedca7178b3d573f0ab",
    "filename": "b4830736a1d78bedca7178b3d573f0ab.mp3",
    "bytes": 59520
  },
  {
    "text": "পানিশূন্যতার লক্ষণ (চোখ গর্তে, ঠোঁট শুকনো)?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "83677aa6de4dc5bb24ae4ff779c08a74",
    "filename": "83677aa6de4dc5bb24ae4ff779c08a74.mp3",
    "bytes": 22560
  },
  {
    "text": "Severe dehydration = RED. Start ORS immediately. Refer to FRU for IV fluids. Do not delay referral.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "129e113ea1bd872573b2f1271fcbe596",
    "filename": "129e113ea1bd872573b2f1271fcbe596.mp3",
    "bytes": 39168
  },
  {
    "text": "ওজন বয়সের তুলনায় অনেক কম?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "adb24fa4d629d20b4eb6cc16366caee4",
    "filename": "adb24fa4d629d20b4eb6cc16366caee4.mp3",
    "bytes": 11904
  },
  {
    "text": "Measure MUAC. MUAC < 11.5 cm or oedema = SAM → RED, refer NRC. MUAC 11.5–12.5 cm = MAM → YELLOW, refer ICDS/NRC for RUTF. MUAC > 12.5 cm = GREEN, counsel on feeding.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "fc747dd7763509bc26df44afb67f49b8",
    "filename": "fc747dd7763509bc26df44afb67f49b8.mp3",
    "bytes": 191136
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশু খাওয়া-দাওয়া একদম বন্ধ করে দিয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c87efad36744ca8b6c2430efd470bcad",
    "filename": "c87efad36744ca8b6c2430efd470bcad.mp3",
    "bytes": 13824
  },
  {
    "text": "Any feeding refusal in infant < 2 months = RED hard-stop. Refer FRU immediately.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7c2b940127288b30c0eb1a5fbfc2a6bd",
    "filename": "7c2b940127288b30c0eb1a5fbfc2a6bd.mp3",
    "bytes": 33408
  },
  {
    "text": "তিন দিনের বেশি জ্বর চলছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7257659d731ea2e75aa322b8a80c86e9",
    "filename": "7257659d731ea2e75aa322b8a80c86e9.mp3",
    "bytes": 11328
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to PHC/FRU same day. Infants < 3 months with any fever = RED hard-stop.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "670072a48148b1526097b90c62902c63",
    "filename": "670072a48148b1526097b90c62902c63.mp3",
    "bytes": 28032
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess dehydration. Some dehydration = YELLOW, PHC within 24 h. Severe dehydration = RED, FRU for IV fluids.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d2e02738a91f778adc798ed183e8f7bd",
    "filename": "d2e02738a91f778adc798ed183e8f7bd.mp3",
    "bytes": 64416
  },
  {
    "text": "শ্বাসকষ্ট বা বুকে শব্দ হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c2e532055a82f2c1a7e16ca664f2445b",
    "filename": "c2e532055a82f2c1a7e16ca664f2445b.mp3",
    "bytes": 12864
  },
  {
    "text": "Chest indrawing or stridor in infant = RED, refer FRU immediately. Fast breathing alone (RR ≥ 50) = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e1ca53c60e6a70723ef2cdf8707d4598",
    "filename": "e1ca53c60e6a70723ef2cdf8707d4598.mp3",
    "bytes": 98880
  },
  {
    "text": "Severe dehydration in infant = RED. Start ORS immediately. Refer FRU for IV fluids.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "0b49e9ff3231ce8b5283e2fd9f5d01a1",
    "filename": "0b49e9ff3231ce8b5283e2fd9f5d01a1.mp3",
    "bytes": 28992
  },
  {
    "text": "ওজন বাড়ছে না বা কমে যাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "33c8bf0c73a9045aa077210ce00798f2",
    "filename": "33c8bf0c73a9045aa077210ce00798f2.mp3",
    "bytes": 13344
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to ICDS/AWC for growth monitoring. If MUAC < 11.5 cm = RED, refer NRC. Counsel on complementary feeding after 6 months.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "1ce2e994c2d20c3541670e4c7283b869",
    "filename": "1ce2e994c2d20c3541670e4c7283b869.mp3",
    "bytes": 58272
  },
  {
    "text": "রক্তচাপ বেশি বা মাথা ব্যথা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "4c49367c13be7a346d257b134879aafe",
    "filename": "4c49367c13be7a346d257b134879aafe.mp3",
    "bytes": 13824
  },
  {
    "text": "Pre-eclampsia/eclampsia hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Do not give food/water. Lay on left side during transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "13dc6abb682bbf97f1c761429ad80d36",
    "filename": "13dc6abb682bbf97f1c761429ad80d36.mp3",
    "bytes": 42336
  },
  {
    "text": "পা বা মুখ ফুলে যাচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "88aba1debb17481e8e6583d03630a9d5",
    "filename": "88aba1debb17481e8e6583d03630a9d5.mp3",
    "bytes": 10656
  },
  {
    "text": "If oedema + headache + BP high = RED (pre-eclampsia). Isolated leg oedema = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h for BP check and urine protein.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "8238223dafdde0d3187d0590b1a7be88",
    "filename": "8238223dafdde0d3187d0590b1a7be88.mp3",
    "bytes": 73632
  },
  {
    "text": "রক্তপাত বা তীব্র পেট ব্যথা?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b03e9d7bebb134615c72b86eac9e3f12",
    "filename": "b03e9d7bebb134615c72b86eac9e3f12.mp3",
    "bytes": 13632
  },
  {
    "text": "APH hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Any bleeding after 20 weeks = emergency. Do not do vaginal examination.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "480612d213aae7153e9d8cc2d00dfc23",
    "filename": "480612d213aae7153e9d8cc2d00dfc23.mp3",
    "bytes": 40896
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর নড়াচড়া কমে গেছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b634ca7eeda48e94f755115d240410f6",
    "filename": "b634ca7eeda48e94f755115d240410f6.mp3",
    "bytes": 11616
  },
  {
    "text": "Refer to FRU/DH same day for fetal monitoring (CTG/Doppler). Absent fetal movement = emergency.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "656ea3d0a851d6337ef44477ac7d7efc",
    "filename": "656ea3d0a851d6337ef44477ac7d7efc.mp3",
    "bytes": 27744
  },
  {
    "text": "তিন মাসের বেশি ANC চেকআপ বাদ গেছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "d184247b57f47d241ac06081aca65ae6",
    "filename": "d184247b57f47d241ac06081aca65ae6.mp3",
    "bytes": 14880
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule ANC visit at PHC within 7 days. Check MCP card. Ensure TT, IFA, calcium supplementation are up to date. Flag for PMSMA if HRP.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a9c423f2091afeecd059b4d2eee4fcf6",
    "filename": "a9c423f2091afeecd059b4d2eee4fcf6.mp3",
    "bytes": 71136
  },
  {
    "text": "চোখে ঝাপসা বা মাথা ঘোরা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b28061d2c1668e188e1f1a1f644f6407",
    "filename": "b28061d2c1668e188e1f1a1f644f6407.mp3",
    "bytes": 13344
  },
  {
    "text": "Eclampsia prodrome hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. Blurred vision + headache + oedema = imminent eclampsia.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "37ee61cdf069f5d0c0fb0c4974f7fdb4",
    "filename": "37ee61cdf069f5d0c0fb0c4974f7fdb4.mp3",
    "bytes": 39936
  },
  {
    "text": "Routine ANC follow-up. Ensure 4 ANC visits (8, 14, 28, 36 weeks). Counsel on IFA (180 tabs), calcium (360 tabs), TT2, diet, birth preparedness. Register on ANMOL.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "0b9f5a8e1afc63ceaf88d9f53b242b48",
    "filename": "0b9f5a8e1afc63ceaf88d9f53b242b48.mp3",
    "bytes": 104352
  },
  {
    "text": "অতিরিক্ত রক্তপাত বা দুর্গন্ধযুক্ত স্রাব?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "110d7407ba2141f2e63184887ad94ed2",
    "filename": "110d7407ba2141f2e63184887ad94ed2.mp3",
    "bytes": 15360
  },
  {
    "text": "PPH hard-stop. Refer to FRU/DH immediately. If trained: bimanual uterine compression. Misoprostol 600 mcg sublingual if within ASHA scope (confirm at sign-off). Do not delay transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ddc207f6e9f4669c47a33112c7aa7084",
    "filename": "ddc207f6e9f4669c47a33112c7aa7084.mp3",
    "bytes": 88704
  },
  {
    "text": "জ্বর বা ঠান্ডা লাগছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "999cfcb7ca313a3e8b4b61039fc385de",
    "filename": "999cfcb7ca313a3e8b4b61039fc385de.mp3",
    "bytes": 10368
  },
  {
    "text": "Puerperal sepsis risk. Fever + foul discharge = RED. Isolated fever day 1–2 = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h. Fever > 38°C after day 2 = RED.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "24f14d7953dcdbcc2fad775a818183cd",
    "filename": "24f14d7953dcdbcc2fad775a818183cd.mp3",
    "bytes": 81792
  },
  {
    "text": "স্তনে ব্যথা, ফোলা বা লাল দাগ?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b9de774bfd0e651c3ed2d0c7679374a3",
    "filename": "b9de774bfd0e651c3ed2d0c7679374a3.mp3",
    "bytes": 16320
  },
  {
    "text": "Mastitis: continue breastfeeding, warm compress, refer PHC within 24 h for antibiotics. If abscess (fluctuant swelling) = RED, refer FRU for I&D.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "e8e3e3ce9669297c538fb5e5502cbb00",
    "filename": "e8e3e3ce9669297c538fb5e5502cbb00.mp3",
    "bytes": 75648
  },
  {
    "text": "পেটে তীব্র ব্যথা বা সেলাইয়ে সমস্যা?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7b17beb3bc8ca2eb3572c38673a5a4bd",
    "filename": "7b17beb3bc8ca2eb3572c38673a5a4bd.mp3",
    "bytes": 13344
  },
  {
    "text": "Wound infection = YELLOW, refer PHC within 24 h. Wound dehiscence or severe pain = RED, refer FRU. Peritonitis signs (rigid abdomen, rebound tenderness) = RED hard-stop.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "934976eb7850d26fcec9211bd6a1c10d",
    "filename": "934976eb7850d26fcec9211bd6a1c10d.mp3",
    "bytes": 106080
  },
  {
    "text": "প্রস্রাবে জ্বালা বা কষ্ট হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "bedbd337445742cbaff6fec0b5b25720",
    "filename": "bedbd337445742cbaff6fec0b5b25720.mp3",
    "bytes": 12864
  },
  {
    "text": "UTI: refer PHC within 24 h for urine culture and antibiotics. If fever + flank pain = pyelonephritis → RED, refer FRU.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b561f67de871cf915add873f7fba2b98",
    "filename": "b561f67de871cf915add873f7fba2b98.mp3",
    "bytes": 64224
  },
  {
    "text": "খুব দুর্বল বা মাথা ঘোরা হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c7a91e0add7fb0381becfee295ff72fa",
    "filename": "c7a91e0add7fb0381becfee295ff72fa.mp3",
    "bytes": 12864
  },
  {
    "text": "Assess pallor (conjunctiva, palms). Severe pallor = anaemia → YELLOW, refer PHC for Hb check. Hb < 7 g/dL or fainting = RED, refer FRU for transfusion.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "5a506771edbe3520990f8a71d34cddfa",
    "filename": "5a506771edbe3520990f8a71d34cddfa.mp3",
    "bytes": 126912
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর বয়স কত মাস?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "7e2d0844284ed00a1db1f79401991069",
    "filename": "7e2d0844284ed00a1db1f79401991069.mp3",
    "bytes": 10176
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule catch-up at nearest session site within 7 days. BCG can be given up to 1 year. OPV/IPV/Pentavalent: give missed dose, continue schedule. Do not restart series.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "3d7a210af1c1a4bba6f7a29ef900c921",
    "filename": "3d7a210af1c1a4bba6f7a29ef900c921.mp3",
    "bytes": 53568
  },
  {
    "text": "কোন টিকা মিস হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "41d9f18ec417b60ce289499cf5d903d1",
    "filename": "41d9f18ec417b60ce289499cf5d903d1.mp3",
    "bytes": 9408
  },
  {
    "text": "Schedule catch-up within 7 days. Measles-1 at 9 months, Vitamin A 1 lakh IU at 9 months. If > 12 months, give MMR instead of measles.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "ef30c0de004a097fb1b6747a71c55f39",
    "filename": "ef30c0de004a097fb1b6747a71c55f39.mp3",
    "bytes": 78816
  },
  {
    "text": "কতদিন আগে টিকা দেওয়ার কথা ছিল?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a5f1d7e03ba5c479af3458767914c1cb",
    "filename": "a5f1d7e03ba5c479af3458767914c1cb.mp3",
    "bytes": 13344
  },
  {
    "text": "Catch-up immunisation. Do not restart series. Give missed dose and continue from where left off. Refer to PHC for catch-up session. Flag on ANMOL for tracking.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a60249c92702fbd681e0396fe56531ba",
    "filename": "a60249c92702fbd681e0396fe56531ba.mp3",
    "bytes": 49344
  },
  {
    "text": "শিশুর কি কোনো অসুস্থতা আছে এখন?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "a601c24dc985fa191cd0db244f8bc7df",
    "filename": "a601c24dc985fa191cd0db244f8bc7df.mp3",
    "bytes": 13344
  },
  {
    "text": "Mild illness (mild fever, cold) = vaccinate as scheduled. Moderate/severe illness = defer vaccination until recovered. Reschedule within 7 days of recovery. Do not miss opportunity for mild illness.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "b5df693324041810bee5344d4c8f1f30",
    "filename": "b5df693324041810bee5344d4c8f1f30.mp3",
    "bytes": 72864
  },
  {
    "text": "১-৫ বছর বয়সী শিশুর বুস্টার ডোজ মিস হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "20346987a15a158507c1b6aa1ed44269",
    "filename": "20346987a15a158507c1b6aa1ed44269.mp3",
    "bytes": 20064
  },
  {
    "text": "DPT booster at 16–24 months. OPV booster at 16–24 months. MMR at 15–18 months. Vitamin A 6-monthly up to 5 years. Schedule catch-up at next session.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "37c6ea2d61f20fa507b10af0141edd34",
    "filename": "37c6ea2d61f20fa507b10af0141edd34.mp3",
    "bytes": 71616
  },
  {
    "text": "অতিরিক্ত রক্তপাত হচ্ছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "83e4b7dfc258b9078be5e15fc76397b3",
    "filename": "83e4b7dfc258b9078be5e15fc76397b3.mp3",
    "bytes": 11328
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Call 108 immediately. Refer FRU/DH ≤ 30 min. Apply uterine compression if postpartum. Do not leave patient alone.",
