    "filename": "a1f14e76488d48e6b53d93563edcc5ae.mp3",
    "bytes": 47616
  },
  {
    "text": "খিঁচুনি বা অজ্ঞান হয়েছে?",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "c3aead7309b0b5ad25f98ef799feab76",
    "filename": "c3aead7309b0b5ad25f98ef799feab76.mp3",
    "bytes": 10848
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Lay on left side, protect airway. Call 108. Refer FRU/DH immediately. If eclampsia: MgSO4 loading dose if within ANM/MO scope. ASHA: do not delay transport.",
    "tone": "question",
    "key": "f58d4950f5a05822226c08daa8702ecc",
    "filename": "f58d4950f5a05822226c08daa8702ecc.mp3",
    "bytes": 72864
  },
  {
