    "filename": "dadeb3c90e399b24b4a46210a66564a5.mp3",
    "bytes": 11136
  },
  {
    "text": "Hard-stop. Call 108. Refer FRU/DH ≤ 30 min. Keep airway clear. If newborn: stimulate, clear airway, bag-mask if available.",
